{"tid":1469262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]武勇找社工或心理專業傾傾","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:25:43.000Z","uid":125817,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5361c31d0d04687da0182022b1b934e79a572943","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:10:47.000Z","msg":"除了道歉，我們也要正視問題。<br />\n就是大家的仇恨得不到疏導，<br />\n有時有點激動了衝動了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議 武勇 或 極憤慨難舒者 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">找社工或心理專業<br />\n傾下計</span></span><br />\n避免仇恨過度沸騰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家一起沈著氣走下去 <br />\n#核爆都唔割</span></span><br />\n<br />\n申利：和理廢中"},{"pid":"0e43b3020dc318182f26dee8a9e7799c44292134","tid":1469262,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"c093b7eab4999dd8e0fa2a279eea176c774029d5","tid":1469262,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n要疏導情緒先繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6214e9ea5ecdabcda7d93a52116f059dc7d1bcf1","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:20:56.000Z","msg":"我在想，<br />\n如果在夢境也有像救護員一樣的<br />\n心理專業主動幫助手足<br />\n治療心理及情緒傷害就太好了 <br />\n<br />\n或者可能不需要太專業，<br />\n但是有一些人充當一個角色叫做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「聊天員」</span></span>"},{"pid":"5be3d42e5e16d71729ce7dd01e9bce3b50c5ea46","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:28:02.000Z","msg":"有人說「已經很克制」<br />\n<br />\n不是克制的問題，<br />\n只是克制最後會壓力爆煲，<br />\n要正視問題，<br />\n就是大家的仇恨得不到疏導"},{"pid":"cc199d038bfde48e459ce86f20ebeae7e1042f2d","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:55.000Z","msg":"有人提意：<br />\n<br />\n三唔識七唔太可行，尤其612仲係暴動定性，如果係追查到身份嘅途逕都唔安全<br />\n<br />\n我覺得充其量<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">電話服務</span></span>OK，衝衝子可以用<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">太空卡</span></span>打"},{"pid":"6be849de19051a71268de24ddd7e50bb74d018c9","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"大家有冇D放鬆心情嘅 歌單 playlist?<br />\n分享下<br />\n<br />\n有隻game music <br />\n&quot;Aquatic Ambiance&quot;<br />\n網上有好多版本的，可以冷靜心神又不磨鬥志<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VG3xuv4VAUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVG3xuv4VAUs&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Q5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=84c1ab7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VG3xuv4VAUs</a>"},{"pid":"45bf075345c8df4f6c597a76ea76b673e45a4645","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"王麗婷 的音樂也很治癒的<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hN09_3jfNFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhN09_3jfNFE&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Q5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e8ef24a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hN09_3jfNFE</a>"},{"pid":"bc4d32569a2de99050c38cefdabaca7080d5f892","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"這只Jazz 音樂也是我經常用來減壓的，效果很好❤️<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL573djNXtwjutD7qRHlvDWvih1Fii7eQ_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL573djNXtwjutD7qRHlvDWvih1Fii7eQ_&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Q5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=fecfd266\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL573djNXtwjutD7qRHlvDWvih1Fii7eQ_</a>"},{"pid":"d66c4a3b131cb55bf71e59e4db0e241e699f7717","tid":1469262,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"或者大家分享下有咩減壓方法<img sr